sentences: Cownie moved to the larger city of Austin, Texas in 2010 to establish his career in comedy, along with fellow Nebraska comic Cody Hustak.
The two would later take first and second place respectively in the prestigious annual Cap City Funniest Person in Austin contest in 2014.
Cownie quickly became an integral part of the Austin comic scene, hosting the Avalanche Comedy showcase from 2013 to 2015.
"Cownie moved again to Los Angeles in 2015 to further his comedy career.
Cownie's debut album I Can't Die was released in 2019.
"In 2019, Cownie starred in the video for "Fashion Forward", a song by Wiebe's side project Drakulas.
Cownie appeared in the 2020 series Munchie Run on the Social Club TV streaming network.
